data.description: Nestled in the the Wellington neighborhood in James City County with a Williamsburg address.  This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac and bordered by a beautiful wooded area that offers lots of privacy this 3,004 sq. ft. home allows for ample space for entertaining guests and/or family. The primary bedroom has a spacious ensuite bathroom with double sinks, a separate garden tub, shower, and a large walk-in closet. The kitchen's layout is both functional and inviting, with a breakfast area, large granite island, desk space, and pantry. The adjacent family room which ensures that those in the kitchen can be part of the lively atmosphere.  A second staircase leads to the expansive bonus room over the garage which could also be used as a 5th bedroom if desired.  Residents of Wellington can enjoy a range of amenities, including a lake, boat ramp, pool, and clubhouse available for rental, adding to the appeal of this desirable community.
